-------------------------------------------------------------------

1) upgrade nodejs to v8

$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install curl
$ curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_10.x | sudo -E bash -
$ sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

-------------------------------------------------------------------

2) install node modules (cd to project root)

$ npm install .

-------------------------------------------------------------------

3) in webstorms, after following tutorial, add the rest of the environment variables (as shown in the png file in project root)